
Overview of noun badge

The noun badge has 2 senses (first 2 from tagged texts)
                                          
1. (3) badge -- (an emblem (a small piece of plastic or cloth or metal) that signifies your status (rank or membership or affiliation etc.); "they checked everyone's badge before letting them in")
2. (2) badge -- (any feature that is regarded as a sign of status (a particular power or quality or rank); "wearing a tie was regarded as a badge of respectability")

